data.description: Home Sweet Home! Welcome to 31 Kerry Drive a home that has been well loved by the same family since 1953!  You will feel right at home as you step up to the front porch leading into the warm & cozy family room w oversize working fireplace w built-in cabinets & closets which flows nicely into the kitchen with solid wood cabinets, pantry, plenty of countertop space and all the appliances to remain for the cook in the family to enjoy. The spacious living room is a wonderful space to entertain especially during the Holiday Season. Three spacious bedrooms & cheerful full bath with linen closet are all nestled together. Home offers efficient gas heating, gas hot water, a full basement that is clean as a whistle & could be easily finished for added living space. Attached one car garage for added convenience that leads out to fenced in back yard w spacious deck a perfect spot to enjoy all your family BBQ's. This home is a true gem for one lucky family to make new memories for years to come!
